attributes.Long form description: The student is assembling a table. They start by inspecting one of the legs, then assembling the middle shelf and one of the legs. They screw the leg onto the shelf, then flip the table over and screw on the second leg. They disassemble the first leg, then reassemble it. They do the same for the second leg, then the third and fourth. Finally, they screw the hex socket heads onto the legs of the table.
